"},{"pid":"21616df161fa7b35934eabb8528d72e59242c44e","tid":423870,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>外國試難好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGCEAL&gt;DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDSE課程cut太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n課程係<br />\n但係份卷淺到guide住你做咁濟"},{"pid":"2bd3b12f6c0d834d30c2309b674178013373dd87","tid":423870,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>外國試難好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGCEAL&gt;DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDSE課程cut太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n課程係<br />\n但係份卷淺到guide住你做咁濟</blockquote><br />\n16年Gce轉左制深左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb029453c38d91378b294054832ab1ad027cf1d","tid":423870,"uid":126831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T20:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>外國試難好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGCEAL&gt;DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDSE課程cut太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n課程係<br />\n但係份卷淺到guide住你做咁濟</blockquote><br />\n16年Gce轉左制深左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ngce考得淺教得深，dse相反"},{"pid":"517c7bb073347c6b5de3cc44a4eeddf942ffad75","tid":423870,"uid":123696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T20:35:58.000Z","msg":"香港DSE(舉例:中文) 5** ~0.9%<br />\n5*+~3.6%<br />\n5+~11%<br />\n<br />\nGCE攞個A*(最高grade)平均~8%<br />\n<br />\n咁你話攞A*係咪易過攞5**/5* <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n份券幾難咪又係拉curve<br />\n唔通仲有人信水平參照 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242f1924f30149ca6a3b635b2958e3692a1f414f","tid":423870,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T20:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港DSE(舉例:中文) 5** ~0.9%<br />\n5*+~3.6%<br />\n5+~11%<br />\n<br />\nGCE攞個A*(最高grade)平均~8%<br />\n<br />\n咁你話攞A*係咪易過攞5**/5* <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n份<span style=\"color: red;\">卷</span>幾難咪又係拉curve<br />\n唔通仲有人信水平參照 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fc3093164779baa65aa3774d03dca1303e349ccb","tid":423870,"uid":76796,"like":4,"dislike":19,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T22:38:59.000Z","msg":"GCE result 會出你份卷幾多分<br />\n香港DSE 就唔理你幾多分，係5** 就5**<br />\n你係professor 想收個90分A*嘅學生定100分A* 嘅學生？<br />\n你係學生想俾人知你low A* 定 high A*?<br />\n無論A* rate 幾高你都係會盡全力考啦<br />\n我做過來人兩邊都讀過，dse 課程真係少，相對上卷就難少少<br />\nGCEAL 課程真係難到痴線，講真讀到會想死，以前paper 出得有format 捉到路。但係依家難咗好多，實用性方面都比DSE好好多。留意GCEAL 就算係Core Maths 都有晒DSE M1/2 嘅野，仲要更多。<br />\n收到風DSE M1/2 諗住cut 走 distribution 同 trigo 嘅微積分，咁樣不如唔好讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我會勸人要讀further math (唔一定要考），因為真係好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能我讀理科先會覺得GCE 難，睇住香港嘅同學就算考DSE 都至少有同friend 出街玩嘅時候，但係我嗰幾年真係連飛機都打唔到<br />\n我之前係oxbridge讀緊medicine,識到嗰香港學生，真係睇得出兩個systems 下嘅分別，諗野方面真係唔夠全面，同埋oxbridge 嘅壓力又係另一個level, 可能GCE 學生適應咗高壓，抗逆能力又係好少少嘅。<br />\n我唔想話DSE 好廢GCE 好勁，我嚟到英國都學識對每樣野要謙卑。我打咁多野都係想話俾睇到呢到嘅你地明白考GCEAL 嘅唔係dse逃兵。講真嗰句逃完咪又係要讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得世界好公平，你有料，就一定有人欣賞你<br />\n<br />\n***17歲前香港讀過，之後一直係英國"},{"pid":"9bbd4b4114a9c28bee65cf14d44de0c1aa091606","tid":423870,"uid":151143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T23:46:26.000Z","msg":"HKAL撚畢晒業冇晒時間打飛機，諗住應該無晒DSE v AL post，估唔到而家GCEAL 都有得拎嚟J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80d5424d9da3ee0bc2b124e13475aca5302f054","tid":423870,"uid":89046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T00:10:30.000Z","msg":"個答案好簡單 公開試既存在理由就係以統一既標準去衡量學術成績，作為升上高等學府既benchmark 。你個國家既高等學府越多，水準越平均，就自然唔洗用更難既syllabus 去篩走啲廢柴，亦都唔需要用較嚴謹既grading 去分出the best of the best<br />\n<br />\n所以大學普及既地方，公開試既難度都較其他地方輕鬆, grading 亦都冇咁strict"},{"pid":"3c2acdf4a00f22c30e3e80d9789dda83ae22d1ca","tid":423870,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>外國試難好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGCEAL&gt;DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDSE課程cut太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n課程係<br />\n但係份卷淺到guide住你做咁濟</blockquote><br />\n16年Gce轉左制深左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ngce考得淺教得深，dse相反</blockquote><br />\n深?年年翻炒有幾深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教得淺，考得淺，拉curve就鬥小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b836d803665cfcdb93bb6cb6f61dff00cca9a4ef","tid":423870,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GCE result 會出你份卷幾多分<br />\n香港DSE 就唔理你幾多分，係5** 就5**<br />\n你係professor 想收個90分A*嘅學生定100分A* 嘅學生？<br />\n你係學生想俾人知你low A* 定 high A*?<br />\n無論A* rate 幾高你都係會盡全力考啦<br />\n我做過來人兩邊都讀過，dse 課程真係少，相對上卷就難少少<br />\nGCEAL 課程真係難到痴線，講真讀到會想死，以前paper 出得有format 捉到路。但係依家難咗好多，實用性方面都比DSE好好多。留意GCEAL 就算係Core Maths 都有晒DSE M1/2 嘅野，仲要更多。<br />\n收到風DSE M1/2 諗住cut 走 distribution 同 trigo 嘅微積分，咁樣不如唔好讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我會勸人要讀further math (唔一定要考），因為真係好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能我讀理科先會覺得GCE 難，睇住香港嘅同學就算考DSE 都至少有同friend 出街玩嘅時候，但係我嗰幾年真係連飛機都打唔到<br />\n我之前係oxbridge讀緊medicine,識到嗰香港學生，真係睇得出兩個systems 下嘅分別，諗野方面真係唔夠全面，同埋oxbridge 嘅壓力又係另一個level, 可能GCE 學生適應咗高壓，抗逆能力又係好少少嘅。<br />\n我唔想話DSE 好廢GCE 好勁，我嚟到英國都學識對每樣野要謙卑。我打咁多野都係想話俾睇到呢到嘅你地明白考GCEAL 嘅唔係dse逃兵。講真嗰句逃完咪又係要讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得世界好公平，你有料，就一定有人欣賞你<br />\n<br />\n***17歲前香港讀過，之後一直係英國</blockquote><br />\ndse根本無得比，cut左太多，同會考差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6e89ff021a7ddaa5fe69efe39e02347e25be3b","tid":423870,"uid":138658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"AL撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369e3899d2d5a611591e747c335c81c3e54ba682","tid":423870,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>AL撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eab4bd85b1d1f3b3f56a469d6503898b9b57e6f","tid":423870,"uid":86418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T01:29:41.000Z","msg":"DSE 學生, 係成個中學生涯連微積分都未掂過<br />\n去到英國唔好揀engineering"},{"pid":"64b783dd4fa30f6cdc4f5449620084ca75b21cc2","tid":423870,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>DSE 學生, 係成個中學生涯連微積分都未掂過<br />\n去到英國唔好揀engineering</blockquote><br />\n返中國讀好中國文化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#"},{"pid":"9b91089f7fbe0cb4f318735996cacd33d7167516","tid":423870,"uid":126831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>DSE 學生, 係成個中學生涯連微積分都未掂過<br />\n去到英國唔好揀engineering</blockquote><br />\n返中國讀好中國文化